OL,3,CLiverpool taxi company take on Uber in
OL,4,Ccourt over cab fare increase
OL,6,FA Liverpool taxi company is preparing
OL,7,Ffor a huge court showdown with Uber in
OL,8,Fa bid to block a judgement that it
OL,9,Fsays could see private hire cab fares
OL,10,Frise by 20%.
OL,12,FThis will be the third time in four
OL,13,Fyears that Liverpool-based Delta has
OL,14,Fgone up against the international ride-
OL,15,Fhailing app, in a case where Uber
OL,16,FBritannia Ltd seek a declaration from
OL,17,Fthe court which would see VAT added to
OL,18,Fthe cost of all private hire vehicle
OL,19,F(PHV) taxi fares outside of London.
