OL,3,CLiverpool taxi company take on Uber in
OL,4,Ccourt over cab fare increase
OL,6,FA 2021 ruling saw VAT added to all
OL,7,Ftaxi rides in London, but Uber is now
OL,8,Fseeking to have that decision come
OL,9,Finto affect nationwide. Uber argue
OL,10,Fthis would level the playing field for
OL,11,Fcustomers across the country.
OL,13,FHowever, companies like Delta have
OL,14,Ffought the move and warned it could
OL,15,Fresult in a 20% rise in fares.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
