OL,3,CLiverpool taxi company take on Uber in
OL,4,Ccourt over cab fare increase
OL,6,FAhead of the court date, Delta Taxis
OL,7,Fand Cardiff-based Veezu have launched
OL,8,Fa new 'Fighting Fund to Protect
OL,9,FPassenger Fares' campaign calling for
OL,10,Fcross-sector and public support as
OL,11,Fthey mount a defence against Uber in
OL,12,Fthe next phase of this long-running
OL,13,Flegal battle, expected in July 2025.
OL,15,FUnlike other modes of transport, which
OL,16,Fbenefit from a zero VAT rating, the
OL,17,Fprivate hire taxi industry remains the
OL,18,Fonly form of transport subject to full
OL,19,FVAT.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
