OL,3,CLiverpool taxi company take on Uber in
OL,4,Ccourt over cab fare increase
OL,6,FDelta Taxis and Veezu are set to meet
OL,7,Fin the Supreme Court ` the highest
OL,8,Fcourt in the land ` to take on Uber in
OL,9,FJuly of this year. As part of the
OL,10,Ftheir campaign, Delta and Veezu have
OL,11,Flaunched a 'Fighting Fund to Protect
OL,12,FPassenger Fares' on CrowdJustice to
OL,13,Fhelp mount the best defence possible.
