OL,3,CLiverpool taxi company take on Uber in
OL,4,Ccourt over cab fare increase
OL,6,FA fundraising target of half a million
OL,7,Fpounds has been set, with the money
OL,8,Fbeing used to help fund the campaign.
OL,9,FCosts and legal fees in excess of one
OL,10,Fmillion pounds have already been
OL,11,Fincurred in this long-running saga,
OL,12,Fwhich are set to rise as they gear up
OL,13,Ffor their third court battle.
OL,15,FPaul McLaughlin, a Delta Taxis
OL,16,Fspokesman, said: "This court case
OL,17,Fcould have massive repercussions for
OL,18,FPHV firms like us using the
OL,19,Ftraditional agency model, which has
OL,20,Fbeen part of British culture for
OL,21,Fgenerations.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
