OL,3,CLiverpool taxi company take on Uber in
OL,4,Ccourt over cab fare increase
OL,6,F"If Uber win, it will add at least 20%
OL,7,Fto the cost of a private hire taxi
OL,8,Ffare outside of London and it will
OL,9,Funfairly penalise passengers, taxi
OL,10,Fdrivers and every other private hire
OL,11,Ffirm in England and Wales. There are
OL,12,Fthousands of traditional private hire
OL,13,Ftaxi firms just like us up and down
OL,14,Fthe country, so the impact will be
OL,15,Ffelt far and wide.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
