OL,3,CLiverpool taxi company take on Uber in
OL,4,Ccourt over cab fare increase
OL,6,F"This really is a David vs Goliath
OL,7,Fmoment ` in this case we're
OL,8,Frepresenting our entire industry and a
OL,9,FGreat British institution, as well as
OL,10,Fthe best interests of taxi drivers and
OL,11,Fpassengers. The potential cost of
OL,12,Fthese changes could be devastating for
OL,13,Fso many people ` we simply cannot let
OL,14,FUber win."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
