OL,3,CLiverpool taxi company take on Uber in
OL,4,Ccourt over cab fare increase
OL,6,FLayla Barke Jones, Dispute Resolution
OL,7,FPartner at the law firm Aaron &
OL,8,FPartners, who represented Delta Taxis
OL,9,Fin the court cases to date and will
OL,10,Frepresent them in the Supreme Court,
OL,11,Fsaid: "We believe it is the most
OL,12,Fvulnerable people in our communities
OL,13,Fwho depend on these taxis that will be
OL,14,Fhardest hit, such as those with
OL,15,Fdisabilities, low-income households
OL,16,Fand older people. It's down to us to
OL,17,Fstop that happening.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
