OL,6,F"There's a lot at stake whichever way
OL,7,Fyou look, but it's our hope that we
OL,8,Fcan once again block this move by Uber
OL,9,Fand protect the operators, drivers and
OL,10,Fpassengers who rely upon traditional
OL,11,Ftaxi firms."
OL,13,FAn Uber spokesperson said: "Uber
OL,14,Fbelieves that there should be
OL,15,Fconsistency throughout the UK to
OL,16,Fensure all operators are required to
OL,17,Fhave the same model."
